data.description: OPEN HOUSE SAT 2/24 11am-1pm and SUN 2/25 1pm-3pm. Location! Location! Location! This single story beauty is nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in sought after Greenbrier. Spacious bedrooms with an abundance of natural light including Primary and attached Ensuite. Expansive eat-in kitchen and separate Dining Room equipped with original brick wood Fireplace. The backyard offers a ton of privacy and the custom Pergola & deck are what truly makes this space feel like your very own Oasis. Neighborhood has multiple paved walking trails, playgrounds, and is convenient to everything! Minutes from Greenbrier Mall, Greenbrier Market Center, Theaters, Restaurants, Schools, and Interstates.
